[[File:Weapon_factory_256.png|right]]The '''Workshop''' is a building in [[Lord of Ultima]]. It allows the construction of siege engines and, if upgraded, increases their construction speed. Placing a Barracks beside a Workshop will also increase recruitment speed.

'''Requirements:''' [[Town Hall]] Level 9








